        "timestamp": "2019-08-08 12:30:26.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\nNote that so far this implementation has been partially verified by\n- the passing original CSIT test which this is based on (but relies on simulators and has some other minor differences) \n- on Dublin env to the extent that Robot container's ability to communicate with SDC-BE and SDC-DCAE-BE has been verified\n- locally with latest testsuite docker image (1.5.0) without real communication to any backends (to verify that the test case is internally consistent and valid)\n\nFinal verification before merging requires full-blown execution on real El Alto lab for not only this test case but also for healthchecks and all distribution test cases for regression. I'm nevertheless setting this ready for review now, just please do not merge this until I have informed of successful final verification",
        "patchset_number": 5
      },
